WEBVTT

00:02.085 --> 00:03.143
<i>Previously on</i> The Vampire Diaries <i>:</i>

00:03.319 --> 00:05.378
For over a century,
I have lived in secret.

00:05.555 --> 00:08.251
Until now.
I know the risk, but I have to know her.

00:08.425 --> 00:10.586
- What are you?
- I'm a vampire.

00:10.760 --> 00:13.923
- He told me about your ex, Katherine.
- You must be Elena.

00:14.097 --> 00:17.396
- How do we look exactly alike?
- I don't want you seeing Elena.

00:17.567 --> 00:21.230
If you don't remove her from your life,
I will kill everyone that she loves.

00:21.404 --> 00:23.235
The Lockwoods are werewolves.

00:23.406 --> 00:26.773
You have to trigger the curse.
Somebody has to die at your hands.

00:26.943 --> 00:29.969
- Tried to kill a werewolf. Failed.
- Now you made an enemy.

00:32.015 --> 00:33.607
Thank you, Mason. Let's do this.

00:33.783 --> 00:35.774
Each with a stake in the heart,
then burn them both.

00:37.420 --> 00:39.854
- Hi, Mom.
- Keep Caroline away from me, please.

00:40.023 --> 00:41.684
- She's your daughter.
- Not anymore.

00:41.858 --> 00:45.157
I'm just looking for this old piece
of my mom's. It's a moonstone.

00:45.328 --> 00:46.852
- Thank you.
- You got it.

00:47.030 --> 00:48.827
I got it.

